snippet.title: Verdun Game Trailer 2017 - PC/XB1/PS4
snippet.description:
WW1 FPS Verdun is now available on X1, PS4 and PC - www.VerdunGame.com

Verdun is the first multiplayer FPS set in a realistic World War One setting. The merciless trench warfare offers a unique battlefield experience, immersing you and your squad in intense battles of attack and defense.
